  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Investment Analyst",
  "description": "<p><strong>Navis Capital Partners</strong> is a Kuala Lumpur based international private/public equity fund management company.</p>\n<p>In line with our continuous growth, we invite suitably qualified and self-motivated individuals to join our Private Equity team at our Singapore office.</p>\n<p><strong>The Job</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Build accurate Financial Model including operating KPIs</li>\n  <li>Assist in due diligence and analysis</li>\n  <li>Develop investment thesis</li>\n  <li>Prepare New Deal alerts and assist in Investment Committee deck preparation</li>\n  <li>Provide industry analysis and deal judgement</li>\n  <li>Provide Analytical support for decision making &amp; assist in company specific initiatives</li>\n  <li>Update team on key industry trends &amp; proactive updating of Senior Deal team</li>\n  <li>Assist in Document Preparation</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Relevant experience in direct equity, investment banking, securities analysis or management consulting with an international or top tier firm</li>\n  <li>Strong analytical skills and structured thinking</li>\n  <li>Proven to contribute and achieve in a team oriented environment</li>\n  <li>Outstanding results from a top, globally recognized university</li>\n  <li>Good command of English</li>\n  <li>Good command of other SE Asian languages is an added bonus</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Interested applicants are invited to apply enclosing your detailed resume stating personal particulars, qualification, and employment history.</strong></p>\n<p><strong>We offer competitive remuneration and excellent career prospects to suitable candidates. You may visit our website at www.naviscapital.com</strong></p>",
